# Band 8 Sample Answer

## Introduction

The pie charts compare the proportions of water used for industrial, agricultural and domestic purposes in six different regions around the world.

**翻译：**
这些饼图比较了世界六个地区在工业、农业和家庭用途方面的用水比例。

---

## Overview

Overall, agriculture accounted for the largest share of water consumption in South America, Africa, Central Asia and South East Asia, whereas industrial use dominated in North America and Europe. In addition, domestic consumption represented the smallest proportion in most regions.

**翻译：**
总体来看，农业用水在南美洲、非洲、中亚和东南亚占据最大比例，而工业用水则在北美和欧洲占主导地位。此外，家庭用水在大多数地区所占比例最小。

---

## Body Paragraph 1

In North America and Europe, industrial activities consumed the majority of water, accounting for 48% and 53% respectively. By contrast, agriculture represented only 39% of water usage in North America and 32% in Europe. Domestic use was comparatively limited in these two regions, standing at 13% in North America and 15% in Europe.

**翻译：**
在北美和欧洲，工业活动消耗了大部分水资源，分别占48%和53%。相比之下，农业用水在北美仅占39%，在欧洲则为32%。家庭用水在这两个地区相对较少，北美和欧洲分别为13%和15%。

---

## Body Paragraph 2

A different pattern can be observed in the remaining four regions, where agriculture was by far the dominant consumer of water. The figures reached 71% in South America, 81% in South East Asia, 84% in Africa and peaked at 88% in Central Asia. Industrial use in these areas was relatively low, particularly in Central Asia and Africa, at only 5% and 7% respectively. Meanwhile, domestic consumption accounted for 19% in South America, compared with 9% in Africa, 7% in Central Asia and 12% in South East Asia.

**翻译：**
其余四个地区则呈现出不同的模式，农业远远成为主要的用水领域。相关比例在南美洲达到71%，东南亚为81%，非洲为84%，并在中亚达到最高的88%。这些地区的工业用水相对较低，尤其是中亚和非洲，分别仅占5%和7%。与此同时，家庭用水在南美洲占19%，相比之下，非洲、中亚和东南亚分别为9%、7%和12%。

---

# ⭐ Band 8 写法解析

## ✅ 这篇为什么像 8 分？

因为它有：

* 清晰 overview
* 分类对比
* 精准数据
* 高级比较结构
* 不重复描述

而不是：
❌ “The percentage is… The percentage is…”

---

# ⭐ 这题最高级的思路

很多学生会：

❌ 一个地区一个地区写

这样逻辑很乱。

真正高分：

# “按特征分类”

---

## 第一类：

工业用水主导：

* North America
* Europe

---

## 第二类：

农业用水主导：

* South America
* Africa
* Central Asia
* South East Asia

这就是：

# IELTS高级分类逻辑

---

