## 表达“占最大比例”

> accounted for the largest share of water consumption

---

## 表达“占主导地位”

> industrial use dominated

---

## 表达“远远是最大的”

> was by far the dominant consumer of water

非常高级。

---

## 表达“达到最高值”

> peaked at 88%

---

## 表达“相对较低”

